---
source: crates/audiomirror-cli/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: output
---
Receive Opus packets over UDP and play them on a local output device.

Example: audiomirror-cli recv --output <device-id> --bind 0.0.0.0:5004

Usage: audiomirror-cli recv [OPTIONS] --output <OUTPUT> --bind <BIND>

Options:
      --output <OUTPUT>
          

      --bind <BIND>
          

      --jitter-mode <JITTER_MODE>
          [default: auto]
          [possible values: auto, min]

      --jitter-max-depth-ms <JITTER_MAX_DEPTH_MS>
          [default: 100]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
